{"name": "cortex_endpoint.CortexEndpoint", "xref": {"fqname": "trulens.providers.cortex.endpoint.CortexEndpoint", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "trulens.providers.cortex.provider.Cortex.snowpark_session", "type": {"name": "Session", "xref": {"fqname": "snowflake.snowpark.Session", "project": "snowflake-snowpark-python"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Snowflake's Cortex COMPLETE endpoint. Defaults to `llama3.1-8b`.\n\nReference: https://docs.snowflake.com/en/sql-reference/functions/complete-snowflake-cortex\n\n!!! example\n\n    === \"Connecting with user/password\"\n        ```python\n        connection_parameters = {\n            \"account\": <account>,\n            \"user\": <user>,\n            \"password\": <password>,\n            \"role\": <role>,\n            \"database\": <database>,\n            \"schema\": <schema>,\n            \"warehouse\": <warehouse>\n        }\n        snowpark_session = Session.builder.configs(connection_parameters).create()\n        provider = Cortex(snowpark_session=snowpark_session)\n        ```\n\n    === \"Connecting with private key\"\n        ```python\n        connection_parameters = {\n            \"account\": <account>,\n            \"user\": <user>,\n            \"private_key\": <private_key>,\n            \"role\": <role>,\n            \"database\": <database>,\n            \"schema\": <schema>,\n            \"warehouse\": <warehouse>\n        }\n        snowpark_session = Session.builder.configs(connection_parameters).create()\n        provider = Cortex(snowpark_session=snowpark_session)\n        ```\n\n    === \"Connecting with a private key file\"\n        ```python\n        connection_parameters = {\n            \"account\": <account>,\n            \"user\": <user>,\n            \"private_key_file\": <private_key_file>,\n            \"private_key_file_pwd\": <private_key_file_pwd>,\n            \"role\": <role>,\n            \"database\": <database>,\n            \"schema\": <schema>,\n            \"warehouse\": <warehouse>\n        }\n        snowpark_session = Session.builder.configs(connection_parameters).create()\n        provider = Cortex(snowpark_session=snowpark_session)\n        ```\n\nArgs:\n    snowpark_session (Session): Snowflake session.\n\n    model_engine (str, optional): Model engine to use. Defaults to `snowflake-arctic`."]}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}]}